      <title>陷入困境的日本首相志愿者将出席道德委员会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/embattled-japan-pm-volunteers-to-appear-before-ethics-panel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄将出席议会道德委员会，试图扭转执政党行贿丑闻的新一页，该丑闻在领导层投票前几个月削弱了他的支持率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/embattled-japan-pm-volunteers-to-appear-before-ethics-panel</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 08:30:20 GMT</pubDate>
